MARCOCCIO--Lucy, (nee Lizzio), born June 15, 1923 in New York City, passed away on January 15, 2007. She was the beloved wife of the late Joseph Marcoccio of Catania, Italy. Lucy was an extensive world traveler and she loved the opera and ballet. She is survived by her younger sister, Angela Lizzio, to whom Lucy was loving and devoted, nephews John and Gary Lizzio, and sister-in-law Nancy Lizzio. She will be missed by . many. Funeral Mass will be held Tuesday, January 22 at 10:00am at the Francis Schervier Nursing Home, 2975 Independence Avenue, Riverdale, New York (718-548-1700).
